        <input id="hdnStartAnimation" name="hdnStartAnimation" type="hidden" value="True"/>
        <script type="text/javascript">
         function theRotator() {
	//Set the opacity of all images to 0
	$('div#rotator ul li').css({opacity: 0.0});
	
	//Get the first image and display it (gets set to full opacity)
	$('div#rotator ul li:first').css({opacity: 1.0});
	
    // Determine if animation should start.
	var StartAnimation = $('input[name=hdnStartAnimation]').val();
	
	//Call the rotator function to run the slideshow, 6000 = change to next image after 6 seconds
	if (StartAnimation == "True")
	{
    	var myInterval = setInterval('rotate()',8000);
    }
    	
	// Each button click needs to show/hide the banner image list item
    $('#rotator_left_button img').click(function() {
        // Find index of clicked button
        var currentItem = $('div#rotator ul li.show');
        var clickIndex = currentItem.index();
        var lastItemIndex = $('div#rotator ul li').last().index();

        // Don't go beyond first item
        if (clickIndex &gt; 0) 
        {
            // Hide previous banner image
            currentItem.css({ opacity: 0.0 }).removeClass('show')

            // Set corresponding banner image index to the current item to show
            $('div#rotator ul li:eq(' + (clickIndex - 1) + ')').css({ opacity: 1.0 }).addClass('show')

            // Stop Animation
            clearInterval(myInterval);
        }
    });

    $('#rotator_right_button img').click(function() {
        // Find index of clicked button
        var currentItem = $('div#rotator ul li.show');
        var clickIndex = currentItem.index();
        var lastItemIndex = $('div#rotator ul li').last().index();

        // Don't go beyond last item
        if (clickIndex &lt; lastItemIndex) 
        {
            // Hide previous banner image
            currentItem.css({ opacity: 0.0 }).removeClass('show')

            // Set corresponding banner image index to the current item to show
            $('div#rotator ul li:eq(' + (clickIndex + 1) + ')').css({ opacity: 1.0 }).addClass('show')

            // Stop Animation
            clearInterval(myInterval);
        }
    });
}

function rotate() {	
	//Get the first image
	var current = ($('div#rotator ul li.show')?  $('div#rotator ul li.show') : $('div#rotator ul li:first'));
	var currentBtn = ($('#dvRotatorButtonContainer ul li.showBtn')?  $('#dvRotatorButtonContainer ul li.showBtn') : $('#dvRotatorButtonContainer ul li:first'));

	//Get next image, when it reaches the end, rotate it back to the first image
	var next = ((current.next().length) ? ((current.next().hasClass('show')) ? $('div#rotator ul li:first') :current.next()) : $('div#rotator ul li:first'));	
	var nextBtn = ((currentBtn.next().length) ? ((currentBtn.next().hasClass('showBtn')) ? $('#dvRotatorButtonContainer ul li:first') :currentBtn.next()) : $('#dvRotatorButtonContainer ul li:first'));	
	
	//Set the fade in effect for the next image, the show class has higher z-index
	next.css({opacity: 0.0})
	.addClass('show')
	.animate({opacity: 1.0}, 1000);

	//Hide the current image
	current.animate({opacity: 0.0}, 1000)
	.removeClass('show');
	
	//Set the li class for identification later
	nextBtn.addClass('showBtn');

	//Hide the old li item class
	currentBtn.removeClass('showBtn');
	
};

$(function() {
	//Load the slideshow
	theRotator();
});
        </script>
